# Build context is repo root, so most of these patterns target the root tree.
# Keep this lean — every byte affects cold-build time.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/*.tsbuildinfo

.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea
.claude

# Workspace packages we don't need in the API image
apps/web
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

# Local env, never ship secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Legacy / migration / docs not needed at runtime
legacy
migration
docs
*.md
!README.md

# Editor + OS noise
**/.DS_Store
*.log

# Harness-helper temp files (CLAUDE.md convention)
**/_*
!**/meta/_journal.json
